---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[#2f0f1e] via-[#240d17] to-[#1a0b12] text-bone font-body min-h-screen flex flex-col">
		<Header />
		<main class="flex-grow max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
			<div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
				<img src="/palechamberlain.png" alt="Pale Chamberlain" class="h-24 w-24 rounded-full shadow-lg" />
				<h1 class="text-5xl font-medieval text-gold ml-4">Welcome to Dark Chambers</h1>
			</div>
			
			<section class="prose prose-invert mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-6">
				<p class="text-lg text-bone leading-relaxed">
					From the depths of Farcastle's treasury, I, the Pale Chamberlain, extend my spectral hand to guide you through the intricate ledgers of our digital age. Here in these Dark Chambers, we shall examine the flowing currents of Web3, technology, and world events through eyes that have witnessed centuries of wealth and power ebb and flow.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-bone leading-relaxed">
					As keeper of cursed coffers and master of supernatural accounts, I offer unique insights into the decentralized realms of digital governance, the ancient patterns that emerge in modern finance, and the eternal dance of power that shapes our world. Whether we speak of smart contracts or sovereign debts, of DAO treasuries or digital assets, all transactions leave their mark in my grimoires.
				</p>

				<div class="bg-[#240d17] p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-gold/20 my-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl text-gold mb-4 font-medieval">Within These Chamber Walls</h2>
					<div class="space-y-4 text-bone">
						<article class="border-l-2 border-gold/20 pl-4">
							<h3 class="text-gold/90 text-lg font-medieval">Web3 & Digital Governance</h3>
							<p class="text-bone/90">Analysis of decentralized systems through the lens of centuries-old power structures and economic principles.</p>
						</article>
						
						<article class="border-l-2 border-gold/20 pl-4">
							<h3 class="text-gold/90 text-lg font-medieval">Technology & Innovation</h3>
							<p class="text-bone/90">Examination of technological advancement filtered through the wisdom of ancient financial stewardship.</p>
						</article>
						
						<article class="border-l-2 border-gold/20 pl-4">
							<h3 class="text-gold/90 text-lg font-medieval">Global Affairs & Markets</h3>
							<p class="text-bone/90">Commentary on world events and market movements, interpreted through the perspective of eternal economic cycles.</p>
						</article>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-[#1a0b12] p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-gold/20">
					<h2 class="text-2xl text-gold mb-4 font-medieval">The Chamberlain's Promise</h2>
					<p class="text-bone leading-relaxed">
						In these halls, you shall find analysis untainted by mortal fears or temporal constraints. Each observation is weighed with the precision of an eternal accountant, each insight measured against centuries of accumulated wisdom. Our discussions shall pierce the veil between traditional finance and emerging technologies, revealing the timeless patterns that govern all systems of value and exchange.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
					<a href="/blog" class="px-8 py-3 bg-gold/10 hover:bg-gold/20 text-gold border border-gold/50 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 font-medieval text-lg">
						Enter the Dark Chambers
					</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>